          <title>
            <string language="en">Blood circulation in the human body</string>

            <string language="x-mt-fr">Circulation de sang dans le corps humain</string>

          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the process of blood circulation in the body. Arteries lead blood away from the heart while veins lead blood to the heart.</string>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt den Prozeß der 
Blutzirkulation im Körper. Arterien bleihaltiges Blut weg vom 
Inneren während bleihaltiges Blut der Adern zum Inneren.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre le processus de la 
circulation de sang dans le corps. Plomb dans le sang d'artères
loin du coeur tandis que plomb dans le sang de veines au coeur.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra o processo da 
circulação do sangue no corpo. Sangue de ligação dos 
arteries away do coração quando sangue de ligação das veias ao 
coração.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra il processo di 
circolazione di anima nel corpo. Piombo nel sangue delle arterie
via dal cuore mentre piombo nel sangue delle vene al cuore.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει τη διαδικασία της 
κυκλοφορίας αίματος στο σώμα. Αίμα μολύβδου αρτηριών 
μακρυά από την καρδιά ενώ αίμα μολύβδου φλεβών στην καρδιά.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra el proceso de la 
circulación de la sangre en el cuerpo. Sangre de terminal de 
componente de las arterias lejos del corazón mientras que sangre de 
terminal de componente de las venas al corazón.</string>
          </description>
